Conclusion

The test scenario demonstrates that:

✅ Mapping configuration is correct.

✅ Unit conversion is correct.

✅ Count metrics reconcile successfully.

✅ Source data totals reconcile mathematically.

❌ Duration metrics are compared using values that resemble individual detail rows rather than aggregated totals.

The evidence strongly indicates a defect in the aggregation-to-comparison pipeline affecting duration fields. Further investigation should focus on validating the aggregated dataset immediately before values are compared and reported.
